column2: SELECT   m.cent_gal_ID as ID,   m.RA as ra,   m.DEC as dec,   n.distance as dist,   o.nprof as nprof,   o.petroR5#_r as Re,   p.band as band,   p.bin as bin,   p.profMean as mean    FROM MyDB.CAM_CATALOGUE AS m   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n   JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.objid    JOIN PhotoProfile AS p ON n.objid=p.objid
